"\n          title=\"back\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n​<br></p>\n<p>&#x3C;레이아웃 정보></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://ko.learnlayout.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://ko.learnlayout.com/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://poiemaweb.com/css3-layout\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://poiemaweb.com/css3-layout</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://poiemaweb.com/css3-box-model\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://poiemaweb.com/css3-box-model</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/wecodeday1/","tagSlugs":["/tag/wecode/","/tag/wecode-1-일차/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-10-01T23:46:37.121Z","description":"Wecode 1일차 정리!","tags":["Wecode","Wecode 1일차"],"title":"Wecode 1일차","socialImage":"/media/image-2.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/wecodeday1/"}}}